<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.3">
<l>paravi vāṉava rētta niṉṟa parama ṉaiparañ cōtiyaik</l>
<l>kuravai kōtta kuḻaka ṉaimaṇi vaṇṇa ṉaikkuṭak kūttaṉai</l>
<l>yarava mēṟi yalaika ṭalama runtu yilkoṇṭa vaṇṇalai</l>
<l>yiravu naṉpaka lumviṭā teṉṟu mēttu taṉmaṉam vaimmiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Highest one who stands while the celestials rever [and] praise [him], the highest light,</l>
<l>the youth who strung the Kuravai, the saphhire-coloured one, the pot dancer,</l>
<l>the majesty who took sleep that abides on the dashing sea mounted on a serpent,</l>
<l>without leaving off be night and by good day always set [your] minds to praising.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
